To setup fast ethernet:
  Go to ROMMON:
    set interface fa1 <ip_addr> <subnet_mask>
    Fa1Enable=1

  Boot up IOS:
    conf t
    int fa1
      ip addr <ip_addr> <subnet_mask>
      no shut
    end


To boot IOS:
  Go to Cat4k ROMMON:
    b tftp://223.255.254.254/tftpboot/ytse/cat4000-is-mz

To set up Cat4k to use new IOS image
  Go to Cat4k ROMMON:
    reload
    priv
    sprom read linecard 1
    sprom write linecard 1
      (change min type to 349, and card index to 111)


To set jitter:
  Go to IOS:
    conf t
    int qam 3/1.1
    no video sessions
    video sessions 10 udp 0xc000 prog 1
    (or video udp 0xc000 prog 1)
    exit

    int gi 3/16
    video udp 0xc000 jitter 100


Before rerunning mpeg_process, make sure you stop the sessions being started
previously:
  test video 3 session 0xc000 stop


Other useful CLIs:
  show int gi 3/16 video


