How to use the embedded CLI
===========================

A. From QNX console

1. Start the process where the message handler is running on (say mpeg_process)
   and put it in background:
   E.g. mpeg_process > log &

2. Start the cli_process:
   cli_process

3. Then type in the command for your module under the pb> prompt.
   To end, type exit.


B. From Cat4k

1. Repeat steps 1 and 2 in A
2. Telnet to the QNX IP address:
   telnet 1.14.80.XX
3. Same as step 3 in A


