Routing live video to eval board:

Tandberg server requires ARP from destination.
Need to route it through a gateway.

Connect server to a routed port, on same sub-net
Send packet to destination on same sub-net of routed port
connected to eval board.
Provide MAC address and encapsulation.

Configuration example:

interface FastEthernet4/15
 no switchport
 ip address 11.11.11.1 255.255.255.0
!
interface FastEthernet4/16
 no switchport
 ip address 12.12.12.1 255.255.255.0
 load-interval 30
!
!   (Not sure we need this!!)
ip route 12.12.12.2 255.255.255.255 FastEthernet4/16
!
arp 12.12.12.2 1234.4321.1234 ARPA


