Embedded CLI:
  Show commands:
            (1) show mux qam#     show each program scheduled packet
                                  number: accumulated, average, max,
                                  and min.
            (2) show idma         show IDMA read/write pointer distance
            (3) show progErr qam# show underflow, schedulea late, and
                                  delivery time backward error count when
                                  mux a program.
            (4) show syncErr qam# show 0x47 sync byte error in packet.
            (5) show pidErr qam#  show PID error in packet header.
            (6) show ccErr qam#   show the CC error between packet.
            (7) show pcktDrop qam# show the number of packet been drop due
                                  to delivery time go backward.

  Clear commands:
            (1) clear mux qam#
            (2) clear idma
            (3) clear progErr qam#
            (4) clear pcktErr qam#

  Input:
    input show counters
    input show session <session_no>
