Download PB image from PB console using PC serial port:
  Need a rollover cable and a serial port adaptor.  Connect the PB console
  port to the PC's serial port.

From PB ROMMON, type:
  dir qnx:
Note the filename.  This is the filename you need to download.
Then download the same file using xmodem:
  xmodem <filename>

From the host, send file using xmodem.
Will take about 10 minute for the image.

